{"tid":2506244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不知就裏，慕名到海南島吃海南雞飯，就上了大當","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T08:19:31.000Z","uid":261647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e40300d23bd86dbfb42bda42494fa94d433b05e","tid":2506244,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210425/XL45ZH4HJJHKJO2AR2DOFZPJ2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210425%2FXL45ZH4HJJHKJO2AR2DOFZPJ2A%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=df696c5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210425%2FXL45ZH4HJJHKJO2AR2DOFZPJ2A%2F&h=cfc785ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210425/XL45ZH4HJJHKJO2AR2DOFZPJ2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：李純恩<br />\n<br />\n海南島去過兩次，兩次都被人請吃「海南雞飯」，吃後感非常強烈，得出的結論，就像全世界最難吃的韓國菜是在韓國那樣，全世界最難吃的海南雞是在海南島。海南島本來只有白切文昌雞，但南洋的「海南雞飯」出名之後，文昌雞就變了海南雞，不知就裏，慕名到海南島吃海南雞飯，就上了大當。海南島的文昌雞做得非常糙，雞肉不鮮，製法粗陋，大塊大塊斬了上碟，口感固然差，見之也影響胃口。根本不是我們吃慣的「海南雞飯」那種滋味。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡海南雞飯做得好吃，且已經有了一套標準，雞嫩飯香，醬油濃郁，食之滋味，泰國也有海南雞飯，雞油飯香味更濃，白斬雞去骨，一份雞飯全是雞肉，油潤鮮美，味道更勝新加坡一籌。兩地海南雞飯都傳來香港，所以香港也有不少餐廳做得出像樣的海南雞飯。以前北角和富道上有家「勝利小廚」，泰式海南雞飯做得一流，常去幫襯，可惜後來關門，不知搬去哪裏了。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，想吃海南雞飯，全世界處處都有，就是不要去海南島，吃過海南島的海南雞飯，就不再想去海南島了。"},{"pid":"cd1ed33118904c1c3c260684f7ee9685aecd902b","tid":2506244,"uid":279321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"等如去星加坡食星洲炒米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876a85f3e7aea11051b4f26304716e8879c85a81","tid":2506244,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:37:40.000Z","msg":"已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdc744759d52c92465165a7eca33577d6266272","tid":2506244,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1ed33118904c1c3c260684f7ee9685aecd902b","tid":2506244,"uid":279321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"等如去星加坡食星洲炒米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"星加坡真係有港式星洲炒米食 味道唔算差<br />\n但係海南島嘅海南式海南雞飯就唔好食"},{"pid":"299c264af5bab37847a1d76d4dfa4660f5fc0f82","tid":2506244,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"首先要搵到個人柒得過7婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7edbbd39664abc4ea2f615fa005d45baaccfdba","tid":2506244,"uid":152559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"299c264af5bab37847a1d76d4dfa4660f5fc0f82","tid":2506244,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"首先要搵到個人柒得過7婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"離地閪一名, 香港人好撚可悲"},{"pid":"1c3bff1ed0501dc7467d7db52a1d354f43b7ae1e","tid":2506244,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7edbbd39664abc4ea2f615fa005d45baaccfdba","tid":2506244,"uid":152559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"299c264af5bab37847a1d76d4dfa4660f5fc0f82","tid":2506244,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"首先要搵到個人柒得過7婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"離地閪一名, 香港人好撚可悲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"百年基業一個閪女人用兩年完全摧毀<br />\n香港氣數已盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf6489fcb6c2a995c84a555135ca763ab317bcd","tid":2506244,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"但有連登仔都話海南雞飯源自海南島<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e9686db1b7e7381b57e23346b14497895da6